"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"From the [art world](https://decrypt.co/85704/nft-artist-beeple-sells-latest-work-29-million-auction) to [gaming](https://decrypt.co/resources/what-is-axie-infinity-the-play-to-earn-nft-game-taking-crypto-by-storm) to [sports](https://decrypt.co/84366/dapper-labs-nft-very-little-resistance-from-sports-nba-nfl), the hype around non-fungible tokens ([NFTs](https://decrypt.co/resources/non-fungible-tokens-nfts-explained-guide-learn-blockchain)) has exploded in 2021. But as the technology matures, NFT developers are exploring their potential to build communities through trustworthiness, longer-term benefits, and opportunities for education and collaboration.\\n\\nFirst came the boom, as [multimillion-dollar artwork sales](https://decrypt.co/60971/beeples-nft-artwork-sells-for-60-3-million-in-christies-auction) grabbed headlines around the world, and holders of early NFTs became [overnight millionaires](https://decrypt.co/77961/someone-bought-cryptopunks-nft-for-443-sold-for-4m-ethereum). Predictably, they were soon followed by a wave of cash-ins and copycats\\n\\nBut it’s the community utility of NFTs that may well have been their saving grace; after weekly trading volumes on major NFT marketplaces [plunged](https://decrypt.co/78660/opensea-ethereum-nft-resurgence-1-2b-monthly-volume) this spring, they rebounded with gusto from July and August. The resurgence was—[in part](https://www.forbes.com/sites/leeorshimron/2021/07/07/the-rebirth-of-nfts-moving-beyond-the-initial-hype/?sh=1328fe447ce2)—attributed to NFT creators successfully building communities around their projects.\\n\\nSoon, people in the public eye were proudly touting their [NFT avatars](https://decrypt.co/79071/cryptopunks-bored-apes-nft-avatar-trend-is-about-community-building) on social media, representing their membership or sense of belonging to a particular collection.\",\"timestamp\":1638511026,\"title\":\"The Next Wave of NFTs is Starting With Community First\"},\"digest\":\"ZwkeHQCl7XWq6SSf8XmEZJBZhZAR38hnDQlMgoAUj5Y\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xbF36Aa0606Df17eC21F5B58DeE6fE0ADCfcBe78c\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"SckZFgcbNbV533mlc3DHGj3eFGXUy0aGlvIfcPqq3NU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"afP9Cm3J5vMVRPFPyw30DT_NQgNdBP9aXTZnwwSM7z4\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"StSvgv4UoC8OTlFIiw_nRc8XZIqv6msJzkBZ361XXHCejmyjMH9OeaxFWW9iAMAdG4eHWVKyLov_yyyl1qK4lQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xe793b3453111b70385dbd30b1a1cf3548b744b50cb81f2a38500d7559d1888093e7f0f10b88a04bd2026d23eb64ce2ed8500b6765d0d77043dc799f9ecbd286f1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"SckZFgcbNbV533mlc3DHGj3eFGXUy0aGlvIfcPqq3NU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"afP9Cm3J5vMVRPFPyw30DT_NQgNdBP9aXTZnwwSM7z4\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"ZwkeHQCl7XWq6SSf8XmEZJBZhZAR38hnDQlMgoAUj5Y\"}"